invitationMessage:
Hello,

I'm sending you an invitation code for the {appName} app.

{appDescription} You can download {appName} here: {appDownloadURL}

With the invitation code you can use {appName} on your device and join our organization {organizationName}.

Once you have installed {appName}, activate your device by clicking this invitation link: {invitationURL}

Or you copy the invitation code {code}, start {appName}, tap on “{joinButtonLabel}” and paste the code.

{expirationHint}
